xtc.parser
Interface InternalElement

All Known Implementing Classes:
ActionBaseValue, BindingValue, CharSwitch, EmptyListValue, GenericActionValue, GenericNodeValue, GenericRecursionValue, GenericValue, ListValue, NullValue, ParseTreeNode, ProperListValue, StringValue, TokenValue, ValueElement
public interface InternalElement

The marker interface for internal grammar elements. Internal grammar elements cannot appear in the abstract syntax tree of a parsed grammar, but rather are added to the tree as part of the packrat parser generator's transformations. Note that any class implementing this interface must also be a Element.
